{"tid":1139723,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【曼聯爭四】摩連奴口中的奇蹟？蘇帥正做給你看…","createTime":"2019-05-05T12:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T00:01:56.000Z","uid":238369,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"621839dd8920b10c6ad5ddf73575bd4c2d91a642","tid":1139723,"uid":238369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"曼聯主場成功反勝修咸頓，由於本輪阿仙奴被熱刺逼和，紅魔得以憑藉今場勝利重返積分榜第四位。不管前路如何，球隊至少已經掌握了爭四的主動權。不但如此，曼聯距離第三名的熱刺也只有3分的差距了。三個月前，曼聯前教練摩連奴曾經口不擇言的表示：「曼聯爭四需要奇蹟」，但如今蘇斯克查正在把這奇蹟展示給全世界看。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/9843957/1/20190303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F9843957%2F1%2F20190303&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2y3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=33c79bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/9843957/1/20190303</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爭撚到未?"},{"pid":"f4ac2d654de248c692c90adbdb53e60523721c5a","tid":1139723,"uid":90410,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:53:22.000Z","msg":"爭到唔係奇蹟<br />\n係神蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961514b02f65abbf7a872d7c2f0bd55e5acac8d9","tid":1139723,"uid":81273,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"咁岩炒撚左摩狗就打d廢隊 之後打一輪勁野又收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e247ed7bebbc9f35cf991b9b4ad8d957a749b990","tid":1139723,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"今晚得曼會贏波<br />\n認真"},{"pid":"c3ef4dbcbcf46bab97302fb642e075343c982949","tid":1139723,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:56:54.000Z","msg":"又叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前四呢<img src=\"/assets/face